    • Method Detail

      • getTurtlePositions

        public Position[] getTurtlePositions()
        Returns the Positions of the compiled code stepwise. If no code is executed, only the start Position is returned.
        Returns:
        Stepwise array of all Positions

      • parseAll

        public Position[] parseAll(java.lang.String[] arguments)
                    throws java.lang.Exception
        Method called from outside to compile the Logo code. Calls all parsers and handles the loop command. Throws SyntaxErrorException, if the code array is empty
        Parameters:
        arguments - Logo code (As linewise String array)
        Returns:
        Stepwise Positions of the Turtle
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - If an error occurs it throws either ParserNotFoundException, SyntaxErrorException, VariableAlreadyInUseException or VariableNotFoundException.
